data.description: Welcome to this 3-bedroom home in the Colquitt Road Estates. 9725 Neely is a lovely gem that boasts exceptional curb appeal and a backyard designed for relaxation and functionality. Situated in a quiet and desirable neighborhood, this home offers a delightful combination of aesthetic charm and practical amenities.From the moment you arrive, you'll be captivated by the charm and character of this beautifully structured residence. Take evening dives into the deep hot tub or start a passion project within the huge barn style shed in the backyard.
